<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>MG</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fff5f7, #fce4ec);
      color: #4a2c2a;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    section {
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5em;
      color: #b76e79;
    }

    p {
      max-width: 500px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .btn {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border: none;
      background: #b76e79;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 20px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #9c5c66;
    }

    .hidden {
      display: none;
      margin-top: 15px;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #6e4b4b;
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      max-width: 300px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- Intro -->
<section>
  <h1>Hi, MG here</h1>
  <p>
    You found this.  
    That already says something about you.
  </p>
  <a href="#story"><button class="btn">Continue</button></a>
</section>

<!-- Story -->
<section id="story">
  <h1>Brief info about me</h1>
  <p>
    I’m the kind of person who doesn’t say much at first…  
    but notices everything.
  </p>
  <p>
    I spend my time solving things most people don’t see—  
    like being on virtual labs,  
    or figuring out where I am in the world on GeoGuessr.
  </p>
  <p>
    Other times, I’m just staring at the sky on Reddit,  
    thinking about planet objects and astrophotography.
  </p>
</section>

<!-- Personality -->
<section>
  <h1>Personality</h1>
  <div class="card">Introverted</div>
  <div class="card">Observant</div>
  <div class="card">Black cat energy</div>
  <div class="card">Unexpectedly funny (eventually)</div>
</section>

<!-- Secrets -->
<section>
  <h1>Tap if you’re curious</h1>

  <button class="btn" onclick="reveal('s1')">What I actually enjoy</button>
  <p id="s1" class="hidden">Cybersecurity puzzles, random maps, and slow coffee bars.</p>

  <button class="btn" onclick="reveal('s2')">What I notice first</button>
  <p id="s2" class="hidden">Details. The small things people think no one sees.</p>

  <button class="btn" onclick="reveal('s3')">What makes me stay</button>
  <p id="s3" class="hidden">Consistency, efforts, empathy, shared-intentions, awareness of emotional investment. Small thoughtful gestures are hawt!</p>
</section>

<!-- Ending -->
<section>
  <h1>Final note</h1>
  <p>
    I don’t expect you to make it this far.  
  </p>
  <p>
    But if you did…  
    maybe we’d get along.
  </p>

  <p style="margin-top:20px;">
    <b>Let’s get to know each other.</b>
  </p>

  <a href="https://instagram.com/allo_cheri" target="_blank">
    <button class="btn">Say hi</button>
  </a>
</section>

<script>
function reveal(id) {
  const el = document.getElementById(id);
  el.style.display = el.style.display === "block" ? "none" : "block";
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
